66
0:03:18.179,000 --> 0:03:19,000
and cognitive dissonance.

67
0:03:20.068,000 --> 0:03:24,000
Now, these sound like big, fancy, academic terms, and they are.

68
0:03:24.585,000 --> 0:03:27,000
But when I describe them, you're going to be like, "Oh!

69
0:03:28.236,000 --> 0:03:31,000
