201
0:09:59.815,000 --> 0:10:01,000
And I'm challenging you all to do that.

202
0:10:01.855,000 --> 0:10:04,000
Take an inventory of your own biases.

203
0:10:04.903,000 --> 0:10:05,000
Where do they come from?

204
0:10:06.212,000 --> 0:10:09,000
Your upbringing, your political perspective, your faith --

205
0:10:09.61,000 --> 0:10:11,000
what shapes your own biases?

206
0:10:13.982,000 --> 0:10:14,000
Then, evaluate your sources --

207
0:10:15.443,000 --> 0:10:17,000
where do you get your information on science?

208
0:10:18.553,000 --> 0:10:19,000
